cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper deals with predicting a user's next cell in cellular networks using machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also uses supervised learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves classification problems, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
